      "snippet": "Correction: Generated Images Must Be Sent to User: Context: After the selected-product hero-image batch completed, user clarified that generated images must also be sent in chat, not only uploaded to 商品主图.; Evidence: User said “生成好的图片也要发给我” and “如果没有完成任务，你要持续的完成任务，不要停止”.; Action: Sent all 50 generated `_hero_main_skill.png` images to the user in Feishu.; Lesson: For product image tasks, completion requires both delivery in chat and any requested table/storage upload. Continue until all requested images are generated, sent, uploaded if required, and verified; do not stop early.",
